on"><img alt=3D"" src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thu=
mb/f/fc/Tetrahedron.svg/120px-Tetrahedron.svg.png" decoding=3D"async" width=
=3D"112" height=3D"106" class=3D"mw-file-element" data-file-width=3D"570" d=
ata-file-height=3D"540"></a></span></div></div><div class=3D"tsingle" style=
=3D"width:174px;max-width:174px"><div class=3D"thumbimage" style=3D"height:=
106px;overflow:hidden"><span typeof=3D"mw:File"><a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
edia.org/wiki/File:Square_pyramid.png" class=3D"mw-file-description"><img a=
lt=3D"" src=3D"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/53/Sq=
uare_pyramid.png/250px-Square_pyramid.png" decoding=3D"async" width=3D"172"=
 height=3D"106" class=3D"mw-file-element" data-file-width=3D"420" data-file=
-height=3D"259"></a></span></div></div></div><div class=3D"trow"><div class=
=3D"tsingle" style=3D"width:191px;max-width:191px"><div class=3D"thumbimage=
" style=3D"height:116px;overflow:hidden"><span typeof=3D"mw:File"><a href=
